NK037(ji)009:1: // dpal ldan mgon po'i skong ba bsdus pa dgra bgegs tshar gcod mnga' gsol dang bcas pa bzhugs so //
NK037(ji)009:2: chos skyong rgyal po dpal ldan mgon po yi //
NK037(ji)009:3: skong bsdus tshig nyung don che kun 'dus la //
NK037(ji)009:4: dam rdzas gtor chen bsham zhing tshil chen gyis //
NK037(ji)009:5: dud pa byas la 'di skad gyer bar bya //
NK037(ji)009:7: ri rab chen po'i pho brang du //
NK037(ji)009:8: chos bzang lha yi 'dun sa'i steng //
NK037(ji)009:9: a mo li ka'i rdo leb dbus //
NK037(ji)009:10: pad+ma nyi ma brtsegs pa'i thog /
NK037(ji)009:11: bi n+aa ya ka pho mo'i steng //
NK037(ji)009:12: mgon po ma h+aa k+aa la ni //
NK037(ji)009:13: sku mdog mthing nag char sprin mdog /
NK037(ji)009:14: tshogs rje tshogs bdag thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)009:15: de yi g.yon du bzhugs pa yi //
NK037(ji)009:16: yum chen yak+sha be t+aa li /
NK037(ji)009:17: nag mo gri gug thod khrag 'dzin //
NK037(ji)009:18: sku la mkha' 'gro'i chas kyis brgyan //
NK037(ji)009:19: chibs su dril rta gwa pa chibs //
NK037(ji)009:20: rlung nag 'tshubs ma'i klong du bzhugs //
NK037(ji)009:22: 'dod yon mchod pas thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)009:23: dpal ldan mgon po nag po yi //
NK037(ji)009:24: sku gsung thugs kyi sprul pa gsum //
NK037(ji)009:25: mgon po sku mchog chen po ni //
NK037(ji)009:26: sngo skya tri sh+aul thod khrag bsnams //
NK037(ji)009:27: khro bo khro mo'i 'khor gyis bskor //
NK037(ji)009:28: sku mchog 'khor bcas thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)009:29: mgon po gsung mchog chen po ni //
NK037(ji)009:30: dmar skya gru tshal thod khrag gsol //
NK037(ji)009:31: lha dmag tshogs kyi 'khor gyis bskor //
NK037(ji)009:32: gsung mchog 'khor bcas thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)009:33: mgon po thugs mchog chen po ni //
NK037(ji)009:34: mthing nag gri gug thod khrag 'dzin //
NK037(ji)009:35: nag po stong dang sha za 'bum gyis bskor //
NK037(ji)009:37: yang cig mgon po'i bka' nyan tshogs //
NK037(ji)009:38: shar phyogs mgon po dpal rab 'chang //
NK037(ji)009:39: smug nag nyi zer zhags pa bsnams //
NK037(ji)009:40: ngang pa rngog nag chibs su chibs //
NK037(ji)009:41: 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)009:42: lho phyogs mgon po legs ldan ni //
NK037(ji)009:43: mthing nag tsan+dana bing chen phyar //
NK037(ji)009:44: rta mchog rdog nag chibs su chibs //
NK037(ji)009:45: 'khor dang bcas pa'i nub phyogs khrag lha mgon po ni //
NK037(ji)009:46: dmar nag tsan+dana gru tshal bsnams //
NK037(ji)009:47: mtshal bu rting dkar chibs su chibs //
NK037(ji)009:48: 'khor dang bcas pa'i byang phyogs mgon po rnam thos sras //
NK037(ji)009:49: g.yas g.yon mdung dar ne'u le 'dzin //
NK037(ji)009:50: seng ge dkar mo chibs su chibs //
NK037(ji)009:51: 'khor dang bcas pa'i shar lho mgon po dzam+b+ha la /
NK037(ji)009:52: sngon po mdung dar ne'u le 'dzin //
NK037(ji)009:53: chu ris sngon po chibs su chibs //
NK037(ji)009:54: 'khor dang bcas pa'i lho nub mgon po re man+ta //
NK037(ji)009:55: mthing nag phyag na ru mtshon bsnams //
NK037(ji)009:56: g.yu rngog sngon po chibs su chibs //
NK037(ji)009:57: 'khor dang bcas pa'i nub byang mgon po sha ba ri //
NK037(ji)009:58: ljang gu rma bya'i rgyal mtshan phyar //
NK037(ji)009:59: bra nag rting dkar chibs su chibs //
NK037(ji)009:60: 'khor dang bcas pa'i byang shar mtshams kyi mgon po ni //
NK037(ji)009:61: phyag na ru mtshon dkar po bsnams //
NK037(ji)009:62: gro bo g.yu rdog chibs su chibs //
NK037(ji)009:63: 'khor dang bcas pa'i steng mgon dung gi thor tshugs can //
NK037(ji)009:64: sku mdog nag po ral gri 'debs //
NK037(ji)009:65: ngang pa rngog dmar chibs su chibs //
NK037(ji)009:66: 'khor dang bcas pa'i 'og phyogs mgon po be t+aa li //
NK037(ji)009:67: sku mdog nag po s+t+wa re bsnams //
NK037(ji)009:68: phag chen gtams pa'i khri la bzhugs //
NK037(ji)009:70: yang cig mgon po'i bka' nyan rnams //
NK037(ji)009:71: shar gyi phyogs kyi mgon po ni //
NK037(ji)009:72: srid pa lha yi gtso bo ste //
NK037(ji)009:73: lha dmag 'bum bcas thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)009:74: lho yi phyogs kyi mgon po ni //
NK037(ji)009:75: gshin rje ya ma r+aa dza ste //
NK037(ji)009:76: gshin rje 'bum bcas thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)009:77: nub kyi phyogs kyi mgon po ni //
NK037(ji)009:78: ma mo srid pa'i rgyal mo ste //
NK037(ji)009:79: ma mo 'bum bcas byang gis phyogs kyi mgon po ni //
NK037(ji)009:80: bdud pho skos rje brang dkar ste //
NK037(ji)009:81: bdud dmag dpung gi shar lho mtshams kyi mgon po ni //
NK037(ji)009:82: btsan rje srog zan dmar po ste //
NK037(ji)009:83: btsan dmag dpung gi lho nub mtshams kyi mgon po ni //
NK037(ji)009:84: rgyal po pe har dgra bla ste //
NK037(ji)009:85: 'gong po 'bum bcas nub byang mtshams kyi mgon po ni //
NK037(ji)009:86: gnod sbyin k+aa la yak+sha ste //
NK037(ji)009:87: gnod sbyin 'bum bcas byang shar mtshams kyi mgon po ni //
NK037(ji)009:88: klu bdud 'chi bdag mgo dgu ste //
NK037(ji)009:89: klu bdud 'bum bcas yang cig mgon po'i bka' nyan pa //
NK037(ji)009:90: lha dmag 'khor bcas dgra bla'i dmag tshogs thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)009:92: ma h+aa k+aa la'i phyi 'khor ni //
NK037(ji)009:93: dpal mgon bdun cu rtsa bdun dang //
NK037(ji)009:94: lha klu gza' chen nor srung dang //
NK037(ji)009:95: phyogs skyong rgyal chen la sogs pa'i //
NK037(ji)009:96: gtsang ris mgon po'i thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)009:97: ma h+aa k+aa la'i bka' sdod ni //
NK037(ji)009:98: dri za me lha gshin rje dang //
NK037(ji)009:99: bden bral chu lha rlung lha dang //
NK037(ji)009:100: gnod sbyin dbang ldan sa bdag dang //
NK037(ji)009:101: nyi zla gza' skar tshogs dang bcas //
NK037(ji)009:102: lha yi tshogs dang klu yi tshogs //
NK037(ji)009:103: srin po ro langs sha za'i tshogs //
NK037(ji)009:105: bskang ngo mchod do thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)009:106: yang cig bka' nyan las mdzad pa //
NK037(ji)009:107: ma mo'i tshogs dang za byed tshogs //
NK037(ji)009:108: gzhon nu mo dang gtogs 'dod mo //
NK037(ji)009:109: rgya chen mo dang sna chen mo //
NK037(ji)009:110: lha chen mo dang srin mo dang //
NK037(ji)009:111: sbrul dang gzigs dang byi la dang //
NK037(ji)009:112: pha bong dred mong phag dang ni //
NK037(ji)009:113: rnga mong la sogs mgo brnyan can //
NK037(ji)009:114: za byed gdug pa chen po'i tshogs //
NK037(ji)009:115: phra men rnams kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)009:116: shan pa rnams kyi thugs dam sprul pa rnams kyi
NK037(ji)009:117: yang sprul rnams kyi yang cig mgon po'i las mkhan
NK037(ji)009:118: rnams // srid pa'i srog gcod nag po dang //
NK037(ji)009:119: sde brgyad re 'byams mched brgyad rnams //
NK037(ji)009:120: bskang ngo mchod do thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)009:121: lo bdud re 'byams bcu gnyis dang //
NK037(ji)009:122: las mkhan srin po rnam bzhi dang //
NK037(ji)009:123: phung sri gri bo bco brgyad rnams //
NK037(ji)009:124: bskang ngo mchod do thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)009:125: de yi 'khor du gyur pa ni //
NK037(ji)009:126: lha 'dre gri bo'i dmag tshogs dang //
NK037(ji)009:127: bran dang yang bran shan pa'i tshogs //
NK037(ji)009:128: srog la rngams pa'i pho nya rnams //
NK037(ji)009:129: bskang ngo mchod do thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)009:130: sdang ba'i dgra bo myur du sgrol //
NK037(ji)009:131: bcol ba'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK037(ji)009:132: ces pa mgon po'i don skong bsdus pa kho bo nam mkha' rin chen gyis sbyar ba mang+ga lam ////
NK037(ji)009:135: dpal ldan mgon po nag po la //
NK037(ji)009:136: sangs rgyas rnams kyis mnga' gsol phyir //
NK037(ji)009:137: sku mdog mthing nag 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK037(ji)009:138: de bzhin bdag gis mnga' gsol lo //
NK037(ji)009:139: dpal ldan mgon po nag po la //
NK037(ji)009:140: rigs gsum mgon pos mnga' gsol phyir //
NK037(ji)009:141: khro gnyer spyan gsum glog ltar 'gyur //
NK037(ji)009:142: de bzhin bdag gis mnga' gsol lo //
NK037(ji)009:143: dpal ldan mgon po nag po la //
NK037(ji)009:144: chos skyong rnams kyis mnga' gsol phyir //
NK037(ji)009:145: dbu skra dmar ser gyen du bardzesa //
NK037(ji)009:146: de bzhin dpal ldan rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas mnga' gsol phyir //
NK037(ji)009:147: dbu la thod skam lnga yis brgyan //
NK037(ji)009:148: de bzhin dpal ldan dkon mchog gsum gyis mnga' gsol phyir //
NK037(ji)009:149: khrims kyi cha lugs gsum dang ldan //
NK037(ji)009:150: de bzhin dpal ldan gshin rje rnams kyis mnga' gsol phyir //
NK037(ji)009:151: zhal gdangs ljags 'dril mche ba gtsigs //
NK037(ji)009:152: de bzhin dpal ldan rgyu skar rnams kyis smin ma sma ra me ltar 'bar //
NK037(ji)009:153: de bzhin dpal ldan bdud kyi rgyal pos dar nag 'jol ber sku la gsol //
NK037(ji)009:154: de bzhin dpal ldan lha srin sde brgyad dpal bo stag gi sham thabs can //
NK037(ji)009:155: de bzhin bdag gis dpal ldan mgon po gza' chen rnams kyis shangs nas gdug pa'i rlung nag 'tshubs //
NK037(ji)009:156: de bzhin dpal dpa' bo rnams kyis tsan+da bing chen g.yas na phyar //
NK037(ji)009:157: de bzhin dpal ldan ma mo rnams kyis thod khrag 'bar ba thugs kar bsnams //
NK037(ji)009:158: de bzhin dpal ldan gnod sbyin rnams kyis rin chen 'bar bas sku la brgyan //
NK037(ji)009:159: de bzhin bdag gis mnga' gsol lo //
NK037(ji)009:160: dpal ldan mgon po nag po la //
NK037(ji)009:161: klu chen rnams kyis mnga' gsol phyir //
NK037(ji)009:162: sbrul gyi chun pos sku la brgyan //
NK037(ji)009:163: de bzhin bdag gis mnga' gsol lo //
NK037(ji)009:164: dpal ldan mgon po nag po la //
NK037(ji)009:165: srin po rnams kyis mnga' gsol phyir //
NK037(ji)009:166: thod rlon phreng ba'i do shal can //
NK037(ji)009:167: de bzhin bdag gis mnga' gsol lo //
NK037(ji)009:168: dpal ldan mgon po nag po la //
NK037(ji)009:169: drang sro nga rnams kyis mnga' gsol phyir //
NK037(ji)009:170: sku yi cha lugs gsum dang ldan //
NK037(ji)009:171: de bzhin bdag gis mnga' gsol lo //
NK037(ji)009:173: srid pa gsum gyis mnga' gsol phyir //
NK037(ji)009:174: sku yi lte ba zur gsum zab //
NK037(ji)009:175: de bzhin bdag gis mnga' gsol lo //
NK037(ji)009:176: dpal ldan mgon po nag po la //
NK037(ji)009:177: me lha rnams kyis mnga' gsol phyir //
NK037(ji)009:178: me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs //
NK037(ji)009:179: de bzhin bdag gis mnga' gsol lo //
NK037(ji)009:180: dpal ldan mgon po nag po la //
NK037(ji)009:181: sa bdag rnams kyis mnga' gsol phyir //
NK037(ji)009:182: bam chen gdan la brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NK037(ji)009:183: de bzhin bdag gis mnga' gsol lo //
NK037(ji)009:184: dpal ldan mgon po nag po la //
NK037(ji)009:185: lha chen rnams kyis mnga' gsol phyir //
NK037(ji)009:186: bswo sgra drag po gsum dang ldan //
NK037(ji)009:187: de bzhin bdag gis mnga' gsol lo //
NK037(ji)009:188: dpal ldan mgon po nag po la //
NK037(ji)009:189: lha min rnams kyis mnga' gsol phyir //
NK037(ji)009:190: cha sgra drag po gsum dang ldan //
NK037(ji)009:191: de bzhin bdag gis mnga' gsol lo //
NK037(ji)009:192: dpal ldan mgon po nag po la //
NK037(ji)009:193: mi rnams kun gyis mnga' gsol phyir //
NK037(ji)009:194: rin chen sna lngas sku la brgyan //
NK037(ji)009:195: de bzhin bdag gis mnga' gsol lo //
NK037(ji)009:196: dpal ldan mgon po nag po la //
NK037(ji)009:197: byol song rnams kyis shes rab ye shes sgron me bsnams //
NK037(ji)009:198: de bzhin bdag gis dpal ldan mgon po nag po la //
NK037(ji)009:199: yi dwags rnams kyis mnga' gsol phyir //
NK037(ji)009:200: rin chen 'bar ba'i gtsug phud can //
NK037(ji)009:201: de bzhin bdag gis mnga' gsol lo //
NK037(ji)009:202: dpal ldan mgon po dmyal ba rnams kyis spyan nas bskal pa'i me chen 'bar //
NK037(ji)009:203: de bzhin bdag gis dpal ldan mgon po b+aa ya be yis shangs nas bskal pa'i rlung chen 'tshubs //
NK037(ji)009:204: de bzhin bdag gis dpal ldan mgon po nag po la //
NK037(ji)009:205: chu lha rnams kyis mnga' gsol phyir //
NK037(ji)009:206: zhal nas bskal pa'i chu chen 'khyil //
NK037(ji)009:207: de bzhin bdag gis mnga' gsol lo //
NK037(ji)009:208: thugs dam rgyud bskul bcol ba'i phrin las mdzod //
